<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 class="hero-title">About <span class="highlight">JJ Blog</span></h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Discover the story behind our passion for sharing knowledge and connecting minds</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="about-content">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-grid">
                <div class="main-content">
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>Our Story</h2>
                        <p>Welcome to JJ Blog, where ideas come to life and stories find their voice. Founded with a passion for sharing knowledge and fostering meaningful connections, our platform serves as a digital haven for writers, thinkers, and curious minds from around the world.</p>
                        
                        <p>What started as a simple idea to create a space for authentic storytelling has evolved into a thriving community where diverse perspectives converge. We believe that every story matters, every voice deserves to be heard, and every reader should have access to content that inspires, educates, and entertains.</p>
                        
                        <p>Our mission is simple yet profound: to democratize content creation and make quality writing accessible to everyone. Whether you're a seasoned writer or someone just starting their journey, JJ Blog provides the tools, platform, and community support you need to share your unique perspective with the world.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
                        <div class="features-grid">
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-pen-fancy"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Quality Content</h3>
                                <p>Curated articles across various topics including technology, lifestyle, travel, and personal development.</p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Community Driven</h3>
                                <p>A vibrant community of writers and readers who engage, share, and support each other's growth.</p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Modern Platform</h3>
                                <p>A sleek, responsive design that works seamlessly across all devices and screen sizes.</p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="feature-card">
                                <div class="feature-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h3>Easy Discovery</h3>
                                <p>Advanced search and categorization features to help you find exactly what you're looking for.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="content-section">
                        <h2>Our Values</h2>
                        <div class="values-list">
                            <div class="value-item">
                                <div class="value-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="value-content">
                                    <h4>Authenticity</h4>
                                    <p>We believe in genuine, honest storytelling that reflects real experiences and perspectives.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="value-item">
                                <div class="value-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="value-content">
                                    <h4>Innovation</h4>
                                    <p>Constantly evolving our platform to provide the best possible experience for our users.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="value-item">
                                <div class="value-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="value-content">
                                    <h4>Community</h4>
                                    <p>Fostering a supportive environment where everyone feels welcome to share and learn.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="value-item">
                                <div class="value-icon">
                                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="value-content">
                                    <h4>Excellence</h4>
                                    <p>Committed to maintaining high standards in content quality and user experience.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Sidebar -->
                <aside class="sidebar">
                    <div class="sidebar-widget">
                        <h3 class="widget-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> By the Numbers
                        </h3>
                        <div class="stats-list">
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <div class="stat-number">1000+</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Articles Published</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Active Writers</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <div class="stat-number">10K+</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Monthly Readers</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <div class="stat-number">25+</div>
                                <div class="stat-label">Countries Reached</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="sidebar-widget">
                        <h3 class="widget-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Get in Touch
                        </h3>
                        <p>Have questions or want to contribute? We'd love to hear from you!</p>
                        <div class="contact-info">
                            <div class="contact-item">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                                <span>jaiswalpiyush040@gmail.com</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-item">
                                <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
                                <span>+91 9142143711</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="contact-item">
                                <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                                <span>827013, Bokaro, Jharkhand, India</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">
                            <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Contact Us
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="sidebar-widget">
                        <h3 class="widget-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i> Join Our Community
                        </h3>
                        <p>Become part of our growing community of writers and readers.</p>
                        <div class="community-actions">
                            <% if (!user) { %>
                                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline btn-full">
                                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Sign Up
                                </a>
                            <% } %>
                            <div class="social-links">
                                <a href="#" class="social-link" title="Facebook">
                                    <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
                                </a>
                                <a href="#" class="social-link" title="Twitter">
                                    <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                                </a>
                                <a href="#" class="social-link" title="Instagram">
                                    <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                                </a>
                                <a href="#" class="social-link" title="LinkedIn">
                                    <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="cta-content">
                <h2>Ready to Share Your Story?</h2>
                <p>Join thousands of writers who have found their voice on JJ Blog. Start your journey today.</p>
                <div class="cta-actions">
                    <% if (!user) { %>
                        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Get Started
                        </a>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <a href="/admin/posts/new" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Write Your First Post
                        </a>
                    <% } %>
                    <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">
                        <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i> Explore Posts
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
